line_chart = base.mark_line().transform_calculate(
    validation = 'if(datum.Date > datetime("2021-03-01"), "True", "False")'
).encode(
    alt.X('Date:T'),
    alt.Y('Close'),
    alt.Color(
        'validation:O', 
        scale=alt.Scale(range=['green', 'orange']),
        legend=alt.Legend(
            values=['Traning', 'Validation'], 
            title='legend')
    )
).properties(
    width=900
)
